  <main class="w-full max-w-2xl px-6 pb-24 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
    <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4">DIGITAL MILLENNIUM COPYRIGHT ACT (DMCA) POLICY</h2>
      
      <p class="mb-4">
        <strong class="text-blue-400">"90 ደቂቃ x 433 ስፖርት"</strong> (the "App") operates as a technical user-interface and media player platform. The App does not host, upload, store, or directly transmit any multimedia content, video streams, or digital television broadcasts on its own servers. All stream networks, server sources, and live match interfaces displayed within the App are publicly available links embedded from third-party external providers and web entities.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-6">We respect the intellectual property rights of others and comply with the safe harbor provisions of the Digital Millennium Copyright Act (DMCA).</p>

      <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide text-xs">1. CONTENT LINKING POLICY</h3>
      <p class="mb-6">As a media player wrapper, the App behaves similarly to a standard web browser. If a copyright owner wishes to restrict the public availability of an embedded link or stream source, the removal request must be directed at the actual third-party host platform hosting the file, as we have no technical control over external streaming entities.</p>

      <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide text-xs">2. TAKEDOWN NOTICES (DMCA REQUESTS)</h3>
      <p class="mb-4">If you are a copyright owner or an authorized agent thereof and believe that any link utilized within our application interface infringes upon your copyrights, you may submit a formal written notification via email. To be valid under 17 U.S.C. § 512(c)(3), your notice must include the following information:</p>
      
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li>A physical or electronic signature of a person authorized to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive right that is allegedly infringed.</li>
        <li>Identification of the copyrighted work claimed to have been infringed, or a representative list of such works.</li>
        <li>Identification of the specific material/station link within our App that is claimed to be infringing, along with clear details or IDs sufficient to permit us to locate the material.</li>
        <li>Information reasonably sufficient to permit us to contact you, such as an address, telephone number, and an electronic mail address.</li>
        <li>A statement that you have a good faith belief that use of the material in the manner complained of is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law.</li>
        <li>A statement that the information in the notification is accurate, and under penalty of perjury, that you are authorized to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive right that is allegedly infringed.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide text-xs">3. CONTACT INFORMATION</h3>
      <p class="mb-4">Please submit all formal DMCA takedown requests and copyright correspondence to our designated compliance contact:</p>
      <div class="bg-black/40 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 space-y-1">
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:matiwosalaye5@gmail.com" class="text-blue-400">matiwosalaye5@gmail.com</a></p>
        <p><strong>Telegram Support:</strong> <a href="https://t.me/MarketingTeam90" class="text-blue-400">t.me/MarketingTeam90</a></p>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-xs italic">Upon receipt of a valid, fully compliant notification containing the elements listed above, we will review the claim and act promptly to remove or disable access to the contested station link within our platform's application dashboard.</p>
    </div>

    <a href="/" class="block w-full text-center py-4 glass-card rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 text-blue-500 font-bold hover:bg-blue-500/10 transition-colors">
      Return to Dashboard
